					ovary broadly ovoid, 2-2.2 by 1.8-2 mm, densely pubescent with hairs 0.1 mm or less, stigma short, not or hardly lobed, 0.1 by 0.4 mm.

Leaves membranous to chartaceous, elliptic-oblong to oblong-lanceolate, 15-35 by 5-11 cm, base short-attenuate to narrowly rounded, apex acute- acuminate;
