					androphore 2-2.5 by 1.5-2(-2.5) mm, entirely with hairs 0.3-0.5 mm;
					synandrium 2.5-2.5 by 1.5-2 mm, gradually narrowed into acute sterile apex, 1-1.5 mm, thecae c. 20.

Female flowers:
